description:
The Steamroller and The Violin is a little masterpiece by Andrei Tarkovsky
A 8 year old boy that plays the violin becomes friends with a macho driver
of a steamroller.
Wonderful photography, touching story.

Mosfilm 1960
Avi, 846 MB, 43 minutes

Enjoy!

